  "title": "Sales Engineer (Metrology/Scientific Products)",
  "description": "<p><em>Our client provides advanced instruments and systems designed for high performance across various industries.</em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Connect with prospective clients to provide tailored semiconductor solutions.</li>\n  <li>Manage the entire sales process, from prospecting to after-sales support.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with global teams and R&amp;D to tailor solutions to customer needs.</li>\n  <li>Drive growth by exploring industry trends and opportunities in the SEA market.</li>\n  <li>Foster and sustain strong client partnerships.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Materials Science or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of sales experience in the <strong>Metrology/Scientific Industry.</strong></li>\n  <li>Good understanding of <strong>semiconductor processes for laboratory equipment uses for failure analysis, quality control and metrology equipment for thin film.</strong></li>\n  <li>Excellent communication, negotiation, and customer relationship skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
